Toll Brothers Inc said itdeclared a two-for-one split of its common stock and said itfiled a registration statement with the Securities and ExchangeCommission for a proposed public offering of 5,700,000 sharesof common as adjusted for the split.    The record date for the split is April 10, and certificatesrepresenting the additional shares will be mailed April 20.    The company said its stock price will be adjusted toreflect the split on April 21. Reuter&#3;